name: Ballerina who wears black
description:
Registration for the JETÉ MAMA AFRICA Project, created and coordinated by Fashion Designer Bianca Lopes. The project consists in valuing and bringing representativeness to black dancers through clothes, pieces and elements that value the black culture and beauty.

Project: Jeté Mama Africa
Designer: Bianca Lopes
Dancer: Flavia Pereira
Photographer: Jessica Tayana

BRASIL 
Curitiba, 2016
